N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 508.6 - Proceedings

State Regulations

An application to become a self-insurer will be deemed a
proceeding as defined in section
500.1
(e) of this

Title. All rules of procedure relating to proceedings, not specifically covered
in this Part, will apply to applications to become a
self-insurer. Notes
